<h3><a name="Attendees"></a> Attendees </h3>
Igor Sfiligoi, Abhishek Rana, Peter Doherty, Mine Altunay, Chander Sehgal, Tanya Levshina, Jeff Foote, Rob Gardner, Alain Roy, Jim Weichel, Sebastien Goasguen
